{"tid":1789833,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"九龍東 斯文圍內足球Group","createTime":"2019-12-19T14:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T10:56:32.000Z","uid":103929,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"14dff97a981a0c0fd157fcc507c3383928678b1d","tid":1789833,"uid":103929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:23:57.000Z","msg":"今次招人係搵一班固定斯文波腳<br />\n<br />\n要求<br />\n1.斯文，懂得收腳（唔係比賽唔使執著）<br />\n2.唔衝撞唔多手，唔亂撞人<br />\n3.有基本功，樂於組織，團隊精神，球品行先<br />\n（衛生波原因係個嗰要返工，避免受傷）<br />\n<br />\n一直選人試腳，踢走過大量獨食、球品差、脾氣差、潛水嘅人，寧缺毋濫。<br />\n<br />\n目前，群組連續2年每個星期六晚九龍區必踢<br />\n除非暴雨特發情況<br />\n群組內全部由陌生人開始認識、已經熟絡<br />\n現在均是固定波腳，人品球品甚佳<br />\n<br />\n年齡層：返工一族<br />\n場地： 7人硬地，九龍東，夜晚，週六<br />\n<br />\n歡迎試腳，合資格才加wts gp<br />\ntelegram：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Relaxball\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FRelaxball&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfFlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=4aafd833\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Relaxball</a>"},{"pid":"c6e02030f241c9fbd30437ed41ece1fcf528c818","tid":1789833,"uid":88940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:24:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://t.me/xmasevehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fxmasevehk&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfFlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=dc590f8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/xmasevehk</a><br />\n唔好意思借位<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">經濟攬炒！香港人果七千萬比人搞啊！佢老母仲OT成九億<br />\n1221<br />\n1224<br />\n1225<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n1224！［行動宜家唔推幾時推？］平安夜 賀佢老母呀！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1789301\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1789301</a>"},{"pid":"e9d2bbe0fe04598c19aada9161ef548ef8d4bcaf","tid":1789833,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T14:24:30.000Z","msg":"【致英國及美國政府的公開信】 《中英聯合聲明》- 條約簽署之第35年<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1789